(22, 'Ranjith (director)', 'f11c4369ffe4db377d4e1a4a24cfcd47.jpg', '', 1, 'Ranjith (born 4 September 1964) is an Indian director, screen writer, and producer known for his work in Malayalam cinema. He is popular for the films Nandanam (2002), Thirakkatha (2008), Paleri Manikyam (2009), Pranchiyettan &amp; the Saint (2010), and Indian Rupee (2011).', 0),
