(83, 'Murali Gopy', '', '', 1, 'Murali Gopy (Malayalam: à´®àµà´°à´³à´¿ à´—àµ‹à´ªà´¿â€) (born on March 4, 1972) is an Indian screenwriter, actor, writer, singer and journalist.[2] He is the son of legendary Malayalam film actor Bharath Gopi and Jayalakshmy.', 0),
(84, 'Anoop Menon', 'a38e7241d92e122b1a501001beafd8da.jpg', '', 1, 'Anoop Menon (born Anoop Gangadharan) is a Indian film actor, screenwriter and lyricist. He worked in television before finding success as an actor in films. He won the 2009 Kerala State Film Award for Second Best Actor and also the 2009 Filmfare Awards for Thirakkatha.[1]', 0),
(85, 'Sidharth Bharathan', '', '', 1, 'Sidharth Bharathan is a Malayalam film actor and director.[1] [2] He is son of Malayalam film Director Bharathan and actress K. P. A. C. Lalitha. He started his career through a successful malayalam film Nammal. He is currently directing the film Nidra in which he is playing the lead role.[3]', 0),
(86, 'Jishnu (actor)', 'd5cb9c369d7bb34ff2daeecda990927a.jpg', '', 1, 'Jishnu Raghavan is a Malayalam film actor. He is the son of Malayalam actor Raghavan.[1] He started his career through a superhit Malayalam film Nammal. He is a mechanical engineer by profession and graduated from NIT Calicut.', 0),
