(89, 'Shweta Menon', 'dbcbf13711594a94e5f757b0dbfe7cf9.png', '', 1, 'Shweta Menon (Malayalam: à´¶àµà´µàµ‡à´¤ à´®àµ‡à´¨àµ‹à´¨àµâ€; born 23 April 1974) is an Indian model, film actress and television anchor. She has predominantly acted in Hindi and Malayalam language films, besides appearing in a number of Tamil productions.', 0),
