(110, 'Mamukkoya', 'c018d5ae3385eee0ed175d9a1e469014.png', '', 1, 'Mamukkoya (born 5 July 1946) is a popular Malayalam comedian actor. His unique usage of Mappila dialect and style marks his presence in the industry. He has acted in more than 450 Malayalam films and is the first winner of State award for Best Comedian in Malayalam cinema.', 0),
