(118, 'Jayaram', 'a11b4653462ed7c8a326d17bbed57ef7.jpg', '', 1, 'Jayaram (born Jayaram Subramaniam on 10 December 1965) is an Indian film actor who predominately acts in Malayalam films and at times in Tamil films.[2] He is also a chenda percussionist and mimic artist.[3]', 0),
(119, 'Shafi (director)', '3447e5a58efc4cefd4a4e6cc1f736fc4.png', '', 1, 'Shafi is an Indian film director who mainly works in Malayalam cinema, known for his comedy films. He has also directed a Tamil film. The director Rafi of the Rafi Mecartin duo is his elder brother. His well known films include Kalyanaraman (2002), Thommanum Makkalum (2005), Mayavi (2007), Chocolate (2007), Chattambinadu (2009), and Marykkundoru Kunjaadu (2010).', 0),
