(186, 'Nisha Aggarwal', '', '', 1, 'Nisha Aggarwal is an Indian film actress. She was born in Mumbai, India to Suman Agarwal and Vinay Agarwal, who has appeared in Telugu language films. Nisha is the younger sister of prominent Indian actress, Kajal Aggarwal.[1] She is best known for featuring alongside Varun Sandesh in Emaindi Ee Vela.[2]', 0),
(187, 'Ezhil', '', '', 1, 'Ezhil is a Tamil film director, who made his debut with the 1999 romantic blockbuster Thulladha Manamum Thullum starring Vijay and Simran. His success streak continued with Pennin Manathai Thottu and Poovellam Un Vasam. [1] All his further movies were huge failures. He will be making a comeback in 2012 after a brief sabbatical.[2]', 0),
