(247, 'Chandan Roy Sanyal', '5b958a1751364d9f7987d45ed6d75ca3.png?303-4', '', 1, 'Chandan Roy Sanyal (born 30 January 1980) is an Indian actor who has acted in Hindi and Bengali films.[1]', 0),
