(61, '\nOne Man Show\n', '', 'The story unfurls itself in the course of a TV game show, much akin to Who Wants to be a Millionaire. Jayakrishnan (Jayaram), the protagonist, comes to take part in the show, hosted by popular filmstar Mukesh. In the course of the show, the host pries into Jayakrishnanâ€™s past and the whole story is unfurled in flashback.', '0000-00-00', 37, 1, 1),
(62, 'Romanian', '', 'Praja is a 2001 Malayalam film by Joshiy starring Mohanlal, N. F. Varghese, Cochin Haneefa and Aishwarya. The film was produced by Joshiy and Renji Panicker under the banner of Mukhyadhara Films. Despite the huge star cast, big budget and heavy initial pull, "praja" - blockbuster of the year.', '0000-00-00', 38, 1, 1),
