(119, '\nOrdinary (film)\n', '119e18cada765f93484b96f62179a9cf92e.jpeg', 'The film follows the adventures of a K.S.R.T.C. bus that travels from Pathanamthitta to the village of Gavi. It received positive critical reviews and turned out to be the first blockbuster film of 2012 in Malayalam cinema.[5]', '0000-00-00', 95, 1, 1),
(120, '\nThe King &amp; the Commissionel\n', '1207a2b21b84aa89252224390f38b0975c5.jpg', 'A Pakistan military group under Maj. Abdul Jalal Rana trespasses Indian waters targeting New Delhi. The plan is intercepted by Dr. Emma John of Intelligence Wing who informs it to her senior Padmabhushan Dr Sudarshan (Nedumudi Venu). Though Dr. Sudarshan tries to contact Home Minister, his Secretary (Sreekumar)snubs him by saying that its crazy to wake the minister up late at night and agrees for a meeting on the next morning. Dr Sudarshan offers Dr Emma a ride back home as it is too late for her to catch the metro train. Kishore Balakrishnan (Vijay Menon), the senior analyst at the agency, is', '2012-03-23', 11, 1, 0),
(121, '\n\n\n\nThis article uses bare URLs for citations. Please consid', '', 'The film tells a story with movie making as the backdrop. Vijayaraghavan appear as the title character of Josettan, who is a senior film producer. Anoop Menon comes up as Saajan Malyath; the still photographer of the movie who is accidentally selected to become the hero of the new movie on production.', '2012-04-20', 0, 1, 1),
(122, 'Pokkiri Raja', '', 'The film revolves around Madhavan Nair who unknowingly kills a teenager and his eldest son. Raja takes the blame and is sentenced to jail for five years. After returning from jail, Raja moves to Madurai and there he rescues the life of the daughter of Maniannai, the village land lord and then Raja turns his right hand and he is named as Madurai Raja. Years later, he started being known as Pokkiri Raja.', '2010-05-07', 2, 1, 1),
(123, '\nRaamanam\n', '', 'The movie is a re-depiction of Smarakasilakal, a celebrated Malayalam novel by Punathil Kunhabdulla.[1][2]', '0000-00-00', 2, 1, 1),
(124, '\nKerala Cafe\n', '', 'Backwater Media &amp; Entertainment Private Limited distributed the film. The film released in Kerala on 29 October 2009.', '2009-10-09', 22, 1, 1),
(125, '\nRitu\n', '', 'Ritu is about young people working in the IT sector. The story follows the lives of three childhood friends: Sunny Immatty (Asif Ali), Sarath Varma (Nishan), Varsha John (Rima). The trio were almost inseparable as friends; they grew up in the same neighborhood in their love, bonding and innocence. They shared a dream of journeying together in life forever.', '0000-00-00', 15, 1, 1),
(126, '\nPatham Nilayile Theevandi\n', '', 'The film tells the story of Sankara Narayanan, a 55-year-old gangman from the Indian Railways. From his teenage days onward he was afraid of the strange voices that talked to him incessantly. To escape the fear, he seeks refuge in alcohol, alienating himself from his family and ending up in an asylum. His son Ramu could never sympathise with a father who had shirked his responsibility as a husband and a father. But Narayanan starts writing letters from the asylum, to which Ramu doesnâ€™t even bother to reply. A young doctor tries to help Sankara Narayanan, for he knows that he can be cured. Th', '2009-11-13', 2, 1, 1),
(127, '\n2 Harihar Nagar\n', '', 'The movie starts with a flashback, in front of a church, in 1980 when the foursome were children. This scene the beginning of their friendship. Thomas Philip (a.k.a. Thomas Kutty) loses money to a scam artist, who responds to his complaints with violence. He is rescued by the other three who respond to his calls of distress. They then invite Thomas Kutty to join their group who, above all, vow never to cheat on one another. The scene is transitioned by the quote "Thomas kutty Vittodaa!" (Thomas kutty, time to run!) once the scam artist brings his friends to return the beating he got.', '2009-04-01', 13, 1, 1),
(128, '\nIvar Vivahitharayal\n', '', 'Vivek (Jayasurya) does his MBA degree from Pondicherry University. Even while as a student, the main ambition of Vivek is to get married as soon as he is back home after his studies. Vivek has a circle of very close friends of four, with whom he discusses everything. Navya Nair appears in a cameo role in the film as his dream wife. Prominent among these friends is Teresa (Samvrutha Sunil). Teresa and other friends advises Vivek not to get married so early and to wait till he finds a job, but Vivek had already made up his mind.', '2009-06-12', 72, 1, 1),
(129, 'Pudhiya Mugam', '', 'Krishnakumar(Prithviraj Sukumaran) is a resident of an agraharam in Kalpathi. Along with his studies, he pursues a career as a percussionist and teaches the mridangam to local students. He is in love with a girlâ€”the daughter of a family friend. Their relationship is not only approved, but supported by both families.', '2009-07-24', 2, 1, 1),
(130, '\nOre Kadal\n', '', 'Ore Kadal was chosen as the inaugural film of the Indian Panorama section at the International Film Festival of India.[1] Ouseppachan won the National Award for the Best Music Director for Ore Kadal.', '0000-00-00', 15, 1, 1),
(131, '\nAshwaroodan\n', '', '', '0000-00-00', 0, 1, 1),
(132, 'Malayalam film', '', 'Baba kalyani was born on 7 January 1949 to Sulochana and Neelakanth Kalyani, a Pune based technocrat and maker of auto components. He attended BITS Pilani, from where he earned a BE(Hons.) in Mechanical Engineering, and later in Massachusetts Institute of Technology where he earned an MS degree.', '0000-00-00', 0, 1, 1),
(133, '\nBalram vs. Tharadas\n', '', 'The movie is set into motion when a large cache of arms is discovered in the land belonging to the local businessman Hussein Sahib (Rizabawa). On investigation, Inspector Varma (Mukesh) finds that Hussein Sahib has no idea about this, but the land was used by someone called Anali Bhaskaran. The Inspector, along with his colleagues Sudhakaran (Jagadeesh) go to arrest Bhaskaran, but they are given a good fight. As the police are being beaten, the screen alternates between a police jeep appearing on the scene and Anali Bhaskaran trying to knife people. Suddenly a hand appears in the scene and bea', '2006-04-28', 135, 1, 1),
(134, '\nBhargavacharitham Moonam Khandam\n', '', 'The plot is inspired from Harold Ramis directed classic black comedy Analyze This (1999) with Robert De Niro playing a mafia don who due to frequent bouts of anxiety attacks gets treated by a famous psychiatrist enacted by the great comedy actor Billy Crystal.[1]', '0000-00-00', 137, 1, 1),
(135, 'Chess (2008 film)', '', 'Chess is a story of young man who is thrown into the deep end where sharks of the society swim with nonchalance.', '2006-07-07', 0, 1, 1),
(136, '\n\n\n\nThis article does not cite any references or sources. Pl', '', 'The style of the movie is non-linearity that is maintained throughout the entire film. The basic story-telling style of Shaji Kailas is spinned on and off by the writer A.K.Sajan.', '0000-00-00', 11, 1, 1),
