(182, '\nInspector Garud\n', '', 'Inspector Garud has Police Inspector Madhavan Kutty (Dileep)as a very corrupt officer who would do any dirty work for money. He became Inspector not through the right channel but by paying 15 lakhs as bribe. So he is now bound on getting his money back through bribes. He is nicknamed Inspector Garud, for getting his job done fast like a hawk.', '2007-01-29', 12, 1, 1),
